item.title: Ranking the Best College Towns for Remote Workers: Data Integration, ETL, Analysis, and Insights with AWS and Mage-AI
item.description: A comprehensive end-to-end data integration and analysis project focused on ranking top college towns for remote workers. It utilizes AWS services, including S3, EC2,RDS and Quicksight, along with the Mage data pipeline tool for ETL operations and Tableau.
